Package: pedigreedata
Title: Pedigree and Phenotype Datasets for Quantitative Genetics
Version: 0.1.0
Date/Publication: 2026
Authors@R: c(
    person("S. Mason", "Garrison", email = "garrissm@wfu.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4804-6003"))
  )
Description: Provides curated pedigree and phenotypic datasets for use in
    quantitative genetics and behavior genetics research. Datasets include
    multi-generation pedigree structures and repeated body weight measurements,
    suitable for demonstrating animal models, heritability estimation, and
    pedigree visualization with packages such as 'BGmisc'
    [Garrison et al. (2024) <doi:10.21105/joss.06203>] and 'ggpedigree'.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/R-Computing-Lab/pedigreedata/,
     https://r-computing-lab.github.io/pedigreedata/
BugReports: https://github.com/R-Computing-Lab/pedigreedata/issues
